00:31:50,550 --> 00:31:52,030
That person is

573
00:31:52,030 --> 00:31:53,830
the biggest venomous snake under heaven.

574
00:31:52,390 --> 00:31:53,730
[Elder Bei He; War Demon]

575
00:31:53,920 --> 00:31:55,110
Sixty years ago,

576
