596
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:42,310
But the one thing that has never changed is our hatred for him.

597
00:32:42,790 --> 00:32:43,590
That's right.

598
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:45,000
All these years,

599
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:47,960
it's been the deep-seated hatred for that fiend

600
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:50,440
that has kept us three alive.

601
00:32:50,890 --> 00:32:53,520
Hearing that the Chief wanted to deal with that person,

602
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:56,350
we are here to guard the mountain

603
00:32:56,640 --> 00:32:58,270
and protect her

604
